         <abstract>
            <p>We analyze the Legendre and Chebyshev spectral Galerkin semi-discretizations of a one dimensional homogeneous parabolic problem with non-constant coefficients. We present error estimates for both smooth and non-smooth data. In the Chebyshev case a limit in the order of approximation is established. On the contrary, in the Legendre case we find an arbitrary high order of convegence.</p>
